title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 26 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 26 2021
description:
Today's daily review is brought to you by Buck, riding solo on Black Friday, which is apparently racist, don't you know?

Rewriting the narrative on what happened in Waukesha, WI, starting with "an SUV killed people."

Alex Berenson discusses the new covid variant and the accompanying travel ban.

The troubling new attitude towards crime, and Buck's personal theft story.
